//ServiceNow Field: "Resolution Details"
ServiceNow has provided the ACL Assessment for Reports application to scan your instance and product an inventory of reports and users that will be affected when the Report View ACLs are enabled. 
Install the ACL Assessment for Reports application from the ServiceNow store. Security Admin Role is required. 

ServiceNow hat die Anwendung „ACL Assessment for Reports“ bereitgestellt, um Ihre Instanz zu scannen und eine Bestandsaufnahme der Berichte und Benutzer zu erstellen, die betroffen sind, wenn die Berichtsansichts-ACLs aktiviert sind.
Installieren Sie die Anwendung „ACL Assessment for Reports“ aus dem ServiceNow-Store. Die Rolle „Sicherheitsadministrator“ ist erforderlich.

//Answer
You can use JavaScript to create a script that generates the desired output for your ServiceNow request. Here's a script that takes the English and German versions of the request and combines them into the "Description" and "Resolution Details" fields:

// English and German versions of the request
const englishRequest = `ServiceNow Field: "Description"
ServiceNow has provided the ACL Assessment for Reports application to scan your instance and product an inventory of reports and users that will be affected when the Report View ACLs are enabled. 
Install the ACL Assessment for Reports application from the ServiceNow store. Security Admin Role is required.`;

const germanRequest = `ServiceNow Field: "Resolution Details"
ServiceNow hat die Anwendung „ACL Assessment for Reports“ bereitgestellt, um Ihre Instanz zu scannen und eine Bestandsaufnahme der Berichte und Benutzer zu erstellen, die betroffen sind, wenn die Berichtsansichts-ACLs aktiviert sind.
Installieren Sie die Anwendung „ACL Assessment for Reports“ aus dem ServiceNow-Store. Die Rolle „Sicherheitsadministrator“ ist erforderlich.`;

// Combine the English and German versions into a single request
const combinedRequest = `${englishRequest}\n\n${germanRequest}`;

// Output the combined request
console.log(combinedRequest);
You can copy and paste this script into a JavaScript environment or use it within a ServiceNow script field to set the "Description" and "Resolution Details" fields as specified in your request. This script combines the English and German versions into a single request with appropriate line breaks.
